                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i1">
                     <rubric>Nomina sacra; incipit of prayers and hymns and their abbreviations; elements of the punctuation signs; elements of Ethiopic numerals.&#xD;
On the incipit page of Text I (fol. 2r), few lines are rubricated alternating with black lines.</rubric>
