                     <note>- About the text “Mäṣḥafä Säʿatat” and the different versions, cp. EAE V,<ref type="mss" corresp="ES501503">501-503</ref>. The text in Ms.<ref type="mss" corresp="ESddm012">DDM-012</ref>seems to belong to the category described as S.2.</note>
                     <note>- The text is similar, but not identical to Mss.<ref type="mss" corresp="ESmr027">MR-027</ref>and<ref type="mss" corresp="ESqmm027">QMM-027</ref>.</note>
